title: 50_nifty_super_magic_trick_Elizabeth_Wood.pdf
description: Ta-dah! The latest in the 50 Nifty Super series is here -- 50 Nifty Super Magic Tricks. Every one of the 50 amazing and fun-to-do tricks features step-by-step instructions, with helpful illustrations when needed. This super edition also includes a glossary of magic terms, practical suggestions for the first-time magician, and everything a midgrader needs to know to put on his or her own magic show.
